# Build artifacts
target/
target-wsl/
*.wasm
artifacts/
# Exception: committed cross-arch determinism artifacts from CI.
!aegis-bench/artifacts/

# Aegis upstream fork clones (CometBFT / Cosmos SDK) — large external repos
